%% Fluxo de telemetria IoT
sequenceDiagram
  participant S as Sensor ESP32
  participant API as POST /api/sensor/telemetria
  participant DB as Base de dados
  participant WS as WebSocket
  participant UI as Browser preview
  S->>API: JSON nivel sensor_id api_key
  API->>DB: LeituraSensor + atualiza Coletor
  API-->>S: 200 OK
  DB-->>WS: emissao salas
  WS-->>UI: atualizacao nivel
